      "content": "That's a good start, really sets the mood. I want to zoom in a bit more on the people to make the threat feel more specific. Can you describe a small group of guys standing on a corner in that area? I want to get a sense of how they look, what they're wearing, and what kind of energy they're giving off so I know how my protagonist should react when they walk past.",
